# Next.js Project Structure

This is a Next.js 15 project using the App Router architecture with shadcn/ui components.

## Key Configuration Files

- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - shadcn/ui configuration with New York style, RSC enabled, and Lucide icons
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies including Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind CSS v4, and shadcn utilities
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with path mapping (@/_ -> ./src/_)

## Project Structure

- `src/app/` - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
  - [layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with Geist fonts
  - [page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Home page component
- `src/lib/` - Utility functions and shared logic
  - [utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) - Tailwind merge utilities for shadcn
- `src/components/` - Reusable React components (to be created)
  - `ui/` - shadcn/ui components (auto-generated via CLI)

## Import Aliases

- `@/components` - Points to `src/components`
- `@/lib` - Points to `src/lib`
- `@/utils` - Points to `src/lib/utils`
- `@/ui` - Points to `src/components/ui`
- `@/hooks` - Points to `src/hooks`

## Technology Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router and React 19
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 with CSS variables
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui (New York style)
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **TypeScript**: Strict mode enabled
- **Fonts**: Geist Sans & Geist Mono
